description:             Biodub is a german producer, musician and DJ. He defines his music as a combination of techno, dub and electronica that is 
equally comfortable on the dancefloor as in the living room. In recent years he released music on labels like Ki Records, 
Tiefenrausch, Samuvar ltd., KanuKanu and Pronounce. His debut album "Reisegefaehrte" was highly acclaimed by an international 
audience and was supported by Troy Pierce, Patrick Lindsey, Osunlade, Anton Zap, Nooncat and Pawas, to name just a few. 
During the last years biodub travelled europe performing his live- and dj-sets. 2013 he played gigs at festivals like Fusion, 
3000Grad or Deepfields.
